items.title: Trump says tariffs coming on steel and aluminium
items.description: Imports of the metals will be hit with a 25% levy, a move that will have the biggest impact in Canada.

items.title: Minister blames monkey for Sri Lanka nationwide power cut
items.description: The outage is yet to be fully fixed, meaning hospitals and other buildings are having to use generators.

items.title: Kosovo PM's party leading but short of majority - partial results
items.description: Albin Kurti's party is on track to come first in Kosovo's general election but may not be able to govern alone.

items.title: Ed Sheeran stopped from busking in Bengaluru by Indian police
items.description: Sheeran says it was a planned performance, but police say they refused permission to prevent congestion.
